7: ## Dependencies\n68: \n69: | Package | Version | Purpose |\n70: |---------|---------|---------|\n71: | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] |\n72: \n73: ---\n74: \n75: ## Implementation Notes\n76: \n77: [TO BE FILLED: Add implementation notes]\n78: \n79: ---\n80: \n81: ## References\n82: \n83: - Spec: `changes/AR-032/spec.md`\n84: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n85: - Proposal: `changes/AR-032/proposal.md`\n86: - Tasks: `changes/AR-032/tasks.md`\n\n(End of file - total 86 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032 вҖ” Dockerfile еӨҡйҳ¶ж®өжһ„е»ә Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-032 вҖ” Dockerfile еӨҡйҳ¶ж®өжһ„е»ә (3 images) |\n| Module | `docker` |\n| Language | Dockerfile |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Describe Dockerfile multi-stage build architecture with 3 images]\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level Architecture\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-032/design.md","time":{"start":1775886177207,"end":1775886177237}}}}
